title: How do I get FaceLock to start working. Again.
content: Once again, facelock has stopped working. Deleted my facelock data and tried setting it up again. It gets to the setup stage to center my face in the inner circle. After that, nothing I do can get it to progress to the next stage of rotating my head to hit all the pieces of the blue circle.
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 4 XL
